---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI for SMBs | Richard Kappel" description="Stop renting software. I help SMBs and founders replace expensive SaaS subscriptions with AI-built custom tools you own forever.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-brand-50/30 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center animate-fade-in">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">AI for SMBs</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Stop Renting Software.<br />Start Owning It.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Your business runs on software you don't own. You're paying monthly for tools you barely use, locked into platforms that don't fit, and handing your data to someone else. There's a better way.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Let's Talk About Your Stack â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Problem -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">The Problem</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">SaaS Bloat Is Draining Your Budget</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Most small businesses pay $500â€“2,000+ per month on SaaS subscriptions. CRMs, project management tools, scheduling apps, invoicing platforms â€” each one charging monthly for features you'll never touch.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            You're locked into their workflows, limited by their design choices, and dependent on their pricing decisions. Your data lives on their servers. And every month, the meter keeps running.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {[
            { amount: '$49â€“199/mo', tool: 'CRM you use at 20% capacity' },
            { amount: '$30â€“99/mo', tool: 'Project management with features you ignore' },
            { amount: '$25â€“79/mo', tool: 'Scheduling tool that could be a simple form' },
            { amount: '$50â€“150/mo', tool: 'Invoicing platform for basic billing' },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-sm whitespace-nowrap">{item.amount}</span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{item.tool}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
          <div class="bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white text-center">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold">That's $6,000â€“18,000+ per year</p>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">For tools you don't fully use and don't own.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">AI-Built Custom Tools You Own Forever</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg">
          AI can now build custom software tailored to exactly how your business works. No monthly fees. Full customization. Your data stays yours.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          {
            icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />',
            title: 'No Monthly Fees',
            desc: 'Pay once to build it. Own it forever. No subscriptions, no price hikes, no vendor lock-in.'
          },
          {
            icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z" />',
            title: 'Built for You',
            desc: 'Every feature designed around your workflow. No bloat, no workarounds, no compromises.'
          },
          {
            icon: '<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />',
            title: 'Your Data, Your Servers',
            desc: 'No third-party access. No data harvesting. Full control over where your information lives.'
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" set:html={item.icon} />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What This Looks Like -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">In Practice</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">What This Looks Like</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg">
          Real scenarios where AI-built tools replace expensive subscriptions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {[
          {
            emoji: 'ðŸ“‡',
            title: 'Custom CRM',
            before: 'Paying $99/mo for a CRM with 200 features â€” using 15.',
            after: 'A lightweight CRM built around your exact sales process. Track leads, follow-ups, and deals your way.',
          },
          {
            emoji: 'ðŸ“…',
            title: 'Scheduling & Booking',
            before: 'Paying $30/mo for Calendly-style booking with limited customization.',
            after: 'Your own booking system with custom availability rules, intake forms, and automatic confirmations.',
          },
          {
            emoji: 'ðŸ“Š',
            title: 'Project Dashboard',
            before: 'Paying $150/mo for project management seats your team barely logs into.',
            after: 'A focused dashboard that tracks what matters to your team â€” nothing more, nothing less.',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="text-3xl">{item.emoji}</span>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">{item.title}</h3>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Before</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.before}</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-600 uppercase tracking-wide">After</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.after}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {[
          { step: '1', title: 'Discovery Call', desc: 'We talk through your business, your tools, and where the pain is.' },
          { step: '2', title: 'Tool Audit', desc: 'I map every SaaS tool you use â€” what it costs, what you actually need from it.' },
          { step: '3', title: 'Build Replacements', desc: 'Using AI, I build custom tools tailored to your exact workflows.' },
          { step: '4', title: 'Deploy & Train', desc: 'Your tools go live. I train your team and make sure everything runs smooth.' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="text-center group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">{item.step}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-lg">
          Book a Call â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Me -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Why Me</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">AI Skills Alone Aren't Enough</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Anyone can prompt an AI to generate code. But knowing what to build, what to prioritize, and how a new tool ripples through the rest of your business â€” that takes experience.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">I've Already Built My Own</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            I'm not theorizing â€” I've replaced my own SaaS subscriptions with custom-built tools. I know what works, what breaks, and what's worth the effort because I've done it myself.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">I Lead a Community of Builders</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            I run Build to Own Club â€” a community of founders and operators building these exact solutions together. The patterns, pitfalls, and wins we discover get fed back into every client engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">20 Years of Business, Not Just AI</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Unlike someone who's just good with AI, I bring two decades of building businesses. I understand the ripple effects â€” how changing one tool impacts your team, your workflows, your customers. I know what to prioritize and what to leave alone.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Build to Own Club -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Community</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Build to Own Club</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          You're not alone in this shift. Join a growing community of founders and operators who are taking back control of their software stack â€” building tools they own, sharing what works, and helping each other move faster.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Get Started â†’
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
  }
</style>
